reviews.text:
Food is good. the design of the restaurant is nice. I ate on the upper floor.. Staffs are nice.
it was a bit dusty (maybe due to the environment of this restaurant which is near a bunch a garage) so i got something on my glass of water but the staff immediately changed my glass.
The food/quality/price is good.
So i recommend it.
Fantastic food and great environment for a romantic meal.

Came here once at lunch and it was good so I came again for dinner.

Ordered seafood paella, was surprised it was a small portion. Rice itself was so-so but seafood was yummy, especially the squid and scallop!!!

We also ordered ribs with sweet potato. Wow absolutely fantastic!!!superb!!!

Was a good experience eating here except that we didn’t understand what took 45minutes to cook for these two dishes... 🙄🙄🙄

Probably one of the best restaurant in town. Price may be on the high side but it was absolutely worth it. We had two of the pork main meals and both came out superb. The pork belly meal must be taken with the accompanied bread else it might be too overwhelming in flavour. The cheese ball dessert deserves the praises given. The place is small, therefore a booking must be made. There is a service charge. Expect to pay HKD 350 per person.
Quality food with interesting interior design

reviews.text:
Food is good. the design of the restaurant is nice. I ate on the upper floor.. Staffs are nice.
it was a bit dusty (maybe due to the environment of this restaurant which is near a bunch a garage) so i got something on my glass of water but the staff immediately changed my glass.
The food/quality/price is good.
So i recommend it.

食物超讚，有驚喜。
蝦膏意粉十分濃郁很香但不會過咸。
牛油果煎雞肉半熟蛋沙律，雞煎得很香脆，整個味道十分夾。
咖哩漢堡扒蛋包飯，單是賣相已經好得，蛋滑咖哩香，漢堡都ok 。
辣酒煮蜆意粉，這個味道是不錯，有辣香，只可惜蜆有沙，我哋個個食到沙沙聲😔，扣一粒星
甜品叫做Shiro ，白色咁解，侍應解釋各部分是什麼食材，好有心機，雖然比較貴，但係好特別，非一般餐廳食到

結論，係長沙灣呢區有間咁正的餐廳，以後lunch 都要多多支持！！
整體食物質素、味道及服務ok，環境不錯，食物擺設也不差，只是限制用餐時間一個半鐘，不算是談天說地的地方，純粹食飯還是可以的。
用心制作的小店，食物質素高，性價比高，員工也很友善，會再回來。
本人購買三百多元的黑牛安格斯牛扒 一 是要半生， 他們就給我全熟的出品， 是不是浪費了我的牛扒？
